    "name": "黄道信条",
    "steam_appid": 2340510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >混沌正在吞噬星辰，宇宙深处的平衡面临崩塌。你将肩负重任，踏上一场拯救银河的史诗旅程。以策略与勇气为武器，释放星座的远古力量，将腐化的混沌驱逐。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/117eaa41d5d8a99daf3ceefb28c8b431.avif?t=1758702261\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个星座英雄都是银河力量的化身，拥有独特的技能与卡组。无论是强大的攻击型英雄，还是擅长控制与辅助的战术型角色，每个英雄都提供全然不同的体验。选择你的星座守护者，以智慧与胆略抗衡腐化的混沌星座！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/9247632a07a67f58cd900b112bdb51eb.poster.avif?t=1758702261\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/9247632a07a67f58cd900b112bdb51eb.webm?t=1758702261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/9247632a07a67f58cd900b112bdb51eb.mp4?t=1758702261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/ef4f757f666993a4cda067a2d5269a6d.avif?t=1758702261\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内拥有上百张风格各异的战斗卡牌，你可以自由搭配组合，构筑属于自己的专属卡组。结合上百种星座恩赐，打造出独一无二的战术体系。面对机制各异的敌人，你需要灵活调整策略、精准应对挑战。无论是稳健防守、步步为营，还是爆发连击、一击制胜，不同的卡组构筑将带来截然不同的战斗体验！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/586f08d31587f78b1aa838808d560ab0.poster.avif?t=1758702261\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/586f08d31587f78b1aa838808d560ab0.webm?t=1758702261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/586f08d31587f78b1aa838808d560ab0.mp4?t=1758702261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/c9543009907696ef75239c54edf2fd9a.avif?t=1758702261\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都从随机生成的房间开始，包含战斗、事件、商店等多种类型。你可以选择避开强敌、积攒资源，也可以直面Boss，搏一把高风险与高回报。路线充满抉择与变数，每一次选择都可能改变战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着冒险不断深入，你将一次又一次沉浸其中，总有新的内容等待你去发掘！全新飞升模式开放了20个难度选项，每个选项都会增加不同的挑战难度。通过灵活调整飞升条件，你可以不断挑战自我，打造最强策略，征服更严峻的试炼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/acc9220ce7ba227c532d6fed1c00923f.poster.avif?t=1758702261\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/acc9220ce7ba227c532d6fed1c00923f.webm?t=1758702261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340510/extras/acc9220ce7ba227c532d6fed1c00923f.mp4?t=1758702261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
